quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,38,"Min mbii …ìe: onon fof njippee aljanna pa'on to lesdi, so nelaa…ìe Am ngaddii e mon peewal, kala dew…óo ngal o goon…óini nelaa…ìe Am oon dee kulol alanaa mo √±ande wattan, …ìe cunotaako e ko yawtiri …ìe to aduna."
  2,39,"So tawii ko …ìeen yeddu…ìe penni kaawese Amen, kam…ìe ngoni yim…ìe jayngol √±ii…ìoo…ìe toon."
  2,40,"Onon …ìi…ì…ìe Isra'il - Annabi Yaakub -ciwtoree mojjereeji Alla …ói O wa…óani on njetton Mo, njokkon humnude aadi Am e mon, goon…óinde Mi e nulaa…ìe Am, e gollirde sariyaaji Am …ói, so on kumnii aadi Am e ko podan-Mi on ko, wano nguurndam mbel…óam e aduna, e njo…ìdi mo∆¥∆¥iri √±ande darnga, kulon Mi Miin tan tawa on pirtataa aadi Am o."
  2,41,"Goon…óinee Kur'aana mbo njippin-Mi dow Muhammad (jkm) te ombo hawri e ko woni nder Tawreeta, ko adii nde ngootaagu Alla e annabaagu Muhammad (jkm) wayleede e mayre, ndeento-…óee wonde adii…ìe yeddude, wotaa mbattitee aayeeje Am …óe coggu pamaru, kulee tikkere e lette Am …óe."
  2,42,"Taa njillindiree goonga - mbo Alla jippini dow nulaa…ìe Mum- e penaale mon …óe, wotaa cuu…óee goonga gar…óo e defte mon …óe cifii…óe Muhammad (jkm) tawa o…óon mbo nganndi o…óon laa…ìaa."
  2,43,"Tottiree juulde timminon dos…óe mayre e ba…ó…óii…ói e sunnaaji mayre, njaltinee asakal jawle mon …óe Alla resndi on, njankinano…óee Alla hawtude e yankinanii…ìe Mo iwde e le√±ol Muhammadu (jkm)."
  2,44,"Holko …ìuri bonde, si o…óon njamira wo…ì…ìe yo ngoon…óu mba…óa ko mo∆¥∆¥i, o…óon njejjita ko'e mon, tawa o…óon njannga Tawreeta, o…óon nganndi ko woni heen e yamiroore rewde diine Alla …óe, e ja…ìande nulaa…ìe Makko, mbela on mbaawaa naftorde hakkillaaji mon …ói?!"
  2,45,"Mballitoree mu√±al e juulde fii kala ge…óe diine e aduna, …ìattinatnde on faade e Alla, O walla on O reena on O ittana on boneeji, nganndee juulde na sa…óti na teddi si wonah e huloo…ìe joomiraawo ma…ì…ìe."
  2,46,"Sabu kam…ìe ngoni yananaa…ìe maa …ìe kawru e Joomiraawo √±ande darnga, maa …ìe ndutto e Makko ngam O yo…ìa …ìe golleeji ma…ì…ìe."
  2,47,"Onon …ìi…ì…ìe Annabiijo Alla Yaakuub (Isra'il) ciftoree mo∆¥∆¥ere diine e aduna nde mba…óan-Mi on, ciftoree wonde Mi …ìurnirii on annabaagal e laamu dow wondii…ìe mon e yonta."
  2,48,"Ndeentoro-…óee lette √±alaande darnga rewde ko yamiraa e accude ko ha…óaa, ndeen √±alaande fittaandu nafataa fittaandu hay huunde, ndu ja…ìantaake tefande go…ó…óo sonaa e yamiroore Alla, coodtiigu ko heewi fof ja…ìetaake, …ìe ngalaa ballo √±ande heen, so tawii tefoowo e coodtiigu ballo alah holno da…óirtee!"